settings.description: My First Level! So This is a fun level to play. There's also a secret ending by going to the chest. To do this, you have to step on the note blocks, Step on P-switch, and run to the chest.

Remake of the first Switch Palace in Super Mario World.
The Bonus Room Checkered Floors/Ceilings are glitched when they are longer than 15 tiles so I had to separate them with Unbreakable SMB1 Blocks.
The first level of Super Mario Land 2: 6 Golden Coins.
Chargin' Chucks lead their fellow Bob-ombs into this tight, grassy water filled course.

A flood has happened in Pipe Maze! There is no explanation but you must get through the maze. It's easy to escape.
 Based on this video: https://youtu.be/BWXblAObfrg
It's all just Tetriminos in this wacky world.
